OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775696638
OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,FBy ITV News Producer Hannah Ward-
OL,7,FGlenton
OL,9,FUS President Donald Trump and Iran
OL,10,Fhave agreed to a two-week ceasefire,
OL,11,Fwith negotiations to begin on Friday
OL,12,Fin Islamabad, Pakistan.
OL,14,FThe ceasefire was mediated by
OL,15,FPakistan's prime minister and its
OL,16,Fmilitary chief and it will see the
OL,17,FStrait of Hormuz reopened.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775696638
OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,FPosting on Truth Social, Trump
OL,7,Fdeclared the agreement a "big day for
OL,8,FWorld Peace", but the ceasefire
OL,9,Frevolves around a 10-point plan
OL,10,Fproposed by Iran, which the president
OL,11,Fdescribed as "a workable basis on
OL,12,Fwhich to negotiate", but the sides
OL,13,Fhave disagreed on its contents before.
OL,15,FITV News explains what is in the
OL,16,Fceasefire plan.
OL,18,FWhat is in Iran's plan?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
