CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775696638
OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,FThe White House has not released the
OL,7,Fdetails of the plan it is working
OL,8,Fwith, but according to semi-official
OL,9,FIranian media outlet, Tasnim News
OL,10,FAgency, it includes the following:
OL,12,F1. The US should commit, in principle,
OL,13,Fto guarantee non-aggression
OL,15,FOn February 28, the US and Israel
OL,16,Flaunched strikes across Iran,
OL,17,Fincluding one that killed Iran's
OL,18,FSupreme Leader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
