OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775696638
OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,FSince then, 1,900 people have been
OL,7,Fkilled in Iran as a result of the
OL,8,Fconflict, including school children.
OL,10,F2. Iran's continued control of the
OL,11,FStrait of Hormuz
OL,13,FThe Strait of Hormuz is a crucial
OL,14,Ftrade passage connecting the Persian
OL,15,FGulf to the Gulf of Oman. A fifth of
OL,16,Fthe world's oil is transported through
OL,17,Fthe waterway.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
