PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775696638
OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,FIran controls its northern side, which
OL,7,Fhas allowed it to prevent the majority
OL,8,Fof vessels from travelling through
OL,9,Fsince the current conflict started.
OL,11,FIran insisted that the waterway was
OL,12,Fstill open, but just not to the US,
OL,13,FIsrael, or any of their allies - Iran
OL,14,Fhas also attacked ships that have
OL,15,Ftried to pass through.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/27
