OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775696638
OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,FThe disruption has caused huge
OL,7,Ffluctuations in global oil and gas
OL,8,Fmarkets and has had knock-on impacts
OL,9,Ffor fuel costs in the UK.
OL,11,FIran's Foreign Minister Abbas Araghchi
OL,12,Fhas said ships would be allowed to
OL,13,Fpass through the Strait over the next
OL,14,Ftwo weeks under coordination from
OL,15,FIran's military "and with due
OL,16,Fconsideration of technical
OL,17,Flimitations".
OL,19,F3. Iran's uranium enrichment right
OL,20,Fshould be accepted
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
