OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775696638
OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,FEnriching uranium is the process of
OL,7,Fchanging the composition of uranium so
OL,8,Fthat it can trigger an explosive chain
OL,9,Freaction. It is needed for a nuclear
OL,10,Fweapon.
OL,12,FIran had a major programme of
OL,13,Fdeveloping uranium enrichment, which
OL,14,Fit kept hidden for years, but it
OL,15,Fsuspended and limited its production
OL,16,Fat various points due to different
OL,17,Finternational agreements.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
