PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775696638
OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,FThe country breached a number of
OL,7,Fagreements over the years and
OL,8,Fofficially pulled out of the Joint
OL,9,FComprehensive Plan of Action (JCPOA),
OL,10,Fwhich limited its uranium projects, in
OL,11,FOctober 2025, declaring that all
OL,12,Frestrictions were void.
OL,14,FIran's nuclear sites have been key
OL,15,Ftargets for Israel and the US,
OL,16,Falthough Iran insists its nuclear
OL,17,Fprogramme is entirely peaceful.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775696638
OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,FIran's government has long insisted
OL,7,Fthat it should have the right to
OL,8,Furanium enrichment. It says it is
OL,9,Fneeded for civil nuclear energy, which
OL,10,Ftypically requires enrichment to 3.67%
OL,11,Fpurity. That was the level Iran was
OL,12,Flimited to under the 2015 JCPOA
OL,13,Fagreement.
OL,15,FIran is believed to have a stockpile
OL,16,Fof uranium enriched to 60% purity,
OL,17,Fwhich is a short technical step away
OL,18,Ffrom the 90% required for nuclear
OL,19,Fweapons.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775696638
OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,FUranium is likely to be one of the
OL,7,Fsticking points for the two sides
OL,8,Fagreeing on a plan.
OL,10,FTrump wrote on Truth Social on
OL,11,FWednesday that the United States "will
OL,12,Fwork closely with Iran", but added:
OL,13,F"There will be no enrichment of
OL,14,FUranium, and the United States will,
OL,15,Fworking with Iran, dig up and remove
OL,16,Fall of the deeply buried (B-2 Bombers)
OL,17,FNuclear "Dust."
OL,19,F4. Lifting of all primary sanctions
OL,26,@yD@IOUyD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
