OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775696638
OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,FPrimary sanctions directly target a
OL,7,Fcountry, for example those imposed by
OL,8,Fthe US, preventing Americans from
OL,9,Fengaging in almost all transactions
OL,10,Fwith Iran, including exporting and
OL,11,Fimporting goods and services, freezing
OL,12,Fassets and travel bans.
OL,14,FThis also includes the sale and
OL,15,Ftransport of Iranian fuel and
OL,16,Frestrictions on Iranian banks.
OL,18,F5. Lifting of all secondary sanctions
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775696638
OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,FSecondary sanctions are designed to
OL,7,Ftarget a country via third parties,
OL,8,Ffor example, non-Americans conducting
OL,9,Fbusiness with Iran, even if it has no
OL,10,Fconnection with the US.
OL,12,FSecondary sanctions imposed by the US
OL,13,Fhave made it difficult for Iran to
OL,14,Fsell its oil globally and have been
OL,15,Fdesigned to make it harder for the
OL,16,Fcountry to develop its nuclear
OL,17,Fcapabilities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775696638
OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,FIran has been the subject of US
OL,7,Fsanctions for decades, and Trump has
OL,8,Factually been forced to ease certain
OL,9,Fsanctions on Iranian oil as a result
OL,10,Fof the recent conflict and its
OL,11,Fsubsequent squeeze on oil markets.
OL,13,FThe sanctions have had huge financial
OL,14,Fimpacts for Iran, and any lifting or
OL,15,Feasing could pump enormous sums of
OL,16,Fmoney into the country's economy.
OL,18,F6. Termination of all UN Security
OL,19,FCouncil resolutions
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
