FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775696638
OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,FUN Security Council (UNSC) resolutions
OL,7,Fare formal expressions of opinion or
OL,8,Fdesires of the United Nations. They
OL,9,Fare official documents adopted by a
OL,10,Fvote of the Council members.
OL,12,FSecurity Council resolutions can
OL,13,Fimpose sanctions aimed at maintaining
OL,14,Fpeace and security and can resolve
OL,15,Fmilitary measures, establish
OL,16,Finternational tribunals, approve
OL,17,Fmandates of peacekeeping forces and
OL,18,Fimpose restrictive measures on
OL,19,Findividuals, such as travel bans and
OL,20,Fasset freezing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775696638
OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,FIran is a member of the United Nations
OL,7,Fand, therefore, is obligated to comply
OL,8,Fwith any UNSC resolutions.
OL,10,FThe Security Council condemned Iran's
OL,11,Fattacks on residential areas and
OL,12,Fcivilians on March 11 and demanded
OL,13,Fthat strikes stop immediately.
OL,15,FIt also demanded that Iran "halt its
OL,16,Fthreats, provocations and actions
OL,17,Faimed at interfering with maritime
OL,18,Ftrade, as well as support to proxy
OL,19,Fgroups across the region".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30816
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775696638
OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,F7. Termination of all IAEA Board of
OL,7,FGovernors resolutions
OL,9,FInternational Atomic Energy Agency
OL,10,F(IAEA) Board of Governors resolutions
OL,11,Fare similar to decisions adopted by a
OL,12,Fbody of members, but they specifically
OL,13,Faddress issues around nuclear safety,
OL,14,Fsecurity and compliance.
OL,16,FIAEA resolutions in recent years have
OL,17,Furged Iran to comply with its
OL,18,Fsafeguarding agreements in terms of
OL,19,Fproviding access to or detailed
OL,20,Finformation about its stockpile of
OL,21,Fenriched uranium.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30817
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775696638
OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,FIran stopped any cooperation with the
OL,7,FIAEA in June 2025 following military
OL,8,Fstrikes by Israel and the US.
OL,10,F8. Payment of compensation for damages
OL,11,Finflicted on Iran
OL,13,FTrump has continually threatened Iran
OL,14,Fwith heavy bombardment, including a
OL,15,Fpromise to "completely obliterate"
OL,16,FKharg Island if a deal wasn't reached,
OL,17,Fas well as the "complete demolition"
OL,18,Fof Iranian bridges and power plants.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30818
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775696638
OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,FThose threats to bomb Iran "back to
OL,7,Fthe Stone Ages" didn't come to
OL,8,Ffruition as an agreement was met
OL,9,Fbefore the ceasefire deadline, but
OL,10,FIran has still suffered heavy damage
OL,11,Fas a result of strikes by the US and
OL,12,FIsrael.
OL,14,FIran's B1 bridge, which is under
OL,15,Fconstruction and reportedly the
OL,16,Ftallest bridge in the Middle East, was
OL,17,Fstruck last week, and Iran has
OL,18,Freported multiple strikes on its
OL,19,Fnuclear facilities, steel factories,
OL,20,Fpower plants and other infrastructure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30819
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775696638
OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,F9. Withdrawal of US combat forces from
OL,7,Fthe region
OL,9,FThe meaning of "combat forces" is
OL,10,Fambiguous, as the US has maintained a
OL,11,Fnetwork of military bases throughout
OL,12,Fthe Persian Gulf since the 1991 Gulf
OL,13,FWar with Iraq.
OL,15,FThe bases act as a security guarantor
OL,16,Fand provide protection for the Gulf
OL,17,FArab nations, and a step-down of
OL,18,Ftroops in the wider region would not
OL,19,Fbe well received by those countries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30820
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775696638
OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,FThe US has roughly 50,000 troops
OL,7,Fstationed in the Middle East, and in
OL,8,Flate March, more than 1,000 US
OL,9,Fsoldiers were preparing to deploy to
OL,10,Fthe region to be available for Iran
OL,11,Foperations, according to reports by
OL,12,FITV News' US partner CNN.
OL,14,FThe vagueness of "combat forces" does
OL,15,Fallow for different interpretations,
OL,16,Fthat could see some troops withdraw
OL,17,Fbut the typical military presence
OL,18,Fremaining in situ.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30821
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775696638
OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,F10. Cessation of the war on all
OL,7,Ffronts, including against the heroic
OL,8,FIslamic resistance in Lebanon
OL,10,FIran's Supreme National Security
OL,11,FCouncil said on Wednesday that while
OL,12,Fit had accepted the two-week
OL,13,Fceasefire, it in no way meant the war
OL,14,Fwas over.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30822
SC,0022
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775696638
OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,F"It is emphasized that this does not
OL,7,Fsignify the termination of the war,"
OL,8,Fthe statement said. "Our hands remain
OL,9,Fupon the trigger, and should the
OL,10,Fslightest error be committed by the
OL,11,Fenemy, it shall be met with full
OL,12,Fforce."
OL,14,FIn Lebanon, where Israel is fighting
OL,15,FIran-backed Hezbollah militants, more
OL,16,Fthan 1,500 people have been killed and
OL,17,Fone million people have been displaced.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@dO]pD@UOU
