OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,FTrump said "almost all" of the
OL,7,Fprevious points of contention have
OL,8,Fbeen agreed upon between the US and
OL,9,FIran, but there would now be a two-
OL,10,Fweek period to allow for the agreement
OL,11,Fto be finalised.
OL,13,F"This will be a double sided
OL,14,FCEASEFIRE! The reason for doing so is
OL,15,Fthat we have already met and exceeded
OL,16,Fall Military objectives, and are very
OL,17,Ffar along with a definitive Agreement
OL,18,Fconcerning Longterm PEACE with Iran,
OL,19,Fand PEACE in the Middle East."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G23/27
