OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,FHow does it compare to what the US
OL,7,Fwants?
OL,9,FThe US has its own 15-point proposal,
OL,10,Fbut the full details have not been
OL,11,Freleased.
OL,13,FIt is thought to include:
OL,15,FOther regional sources have suggested
OL,16,Fthat acknowledgement of Israel's right
OL,17,Fto exist is also among the plan,
OL,18,Faccording to CNN.
