OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,FIran had previously rejected the US'
OL,7,Fplan, with one official describing the
OL,8,Fdemands as "largely excessive,
OL,9,Funrealistic and unreasonable".
OL,11,FTrump said in late March that Iran had
OL,12,Fagreed to "most of" the points.
OL,14,FWhat about Israel?
OL,16,FIsrael is part of the ceasefire and
OL,17,Fwill also suspend bombing against
OL,18,FIran, Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,19,FNetanyahu's office said.
OL,21,FWhat about Lebanon?
