OL,3,CWhat is in Iran's 10-point ceasefire
OL,4,Cplan?
OL,6,FPakistan, which helped to mediate the
OL,7,Fdeal, and others said fighting would
OL,8,Fpause in Lebanon, where Israel has
OL,9,Flaunched a ground invasion against the
OL,10,FIran-backed Hezbollah militant group.
OL,12,FIsrael said it would not. Netanyahu
OL,13,Fsaid early on Wednesday that the deal
OL,14,Fdoesn't cover fighting against
OL,15,FHezbollah in Lebanon. Israel's
OL,16,Fmilitary said later that fighting and
OL,17,Fground operations continue.
OL,19,FTrump did not mention Lebanon in his
OL,20,Fstatements.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G26/27
